# ReplyGraph runs entirely from local config (backend/data/app_settings.json).
# No environment variables are required to run.
#
# Optional: your Anthropic API key for real LLM-drafted replies.
# You normally set this in the app's Settings page (stored locally,
# never committed). If you prefer an env var for development, the key
# lives in backend/data/app_settings.json as "llm_api_key".
#
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
